trans-unit.source: Provides minimal design-time support for <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.ProxyWebPartManager"></xref> controls.
trans-unit.target: Gir støtte for minimal utformingen for <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.ProxyWebPartManager"> </xref> kontroller.

trans-unit.source: The ProxyWebPartManagerDesigner class is identical to the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManagerDesigner> class and provides design-time support for <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.ProxyWebPartManager> controls.
trans-unit.target: Klassen ProxyWebPartManagerDesigner er identisk med den <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManagerDesigner>klasse og gir støtte for utforming for <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.ProxyWebPartManager>Kontroller.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.ProxyWebPartManager> </xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManagerDesigner>

trans-unit.source: It appears on the design surface as a plain gray box showing the name of the class and the ID of the specific <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.ProxyWebPartManager> control.
trans-unit.target: Det vises på utformingsoverflaten som en vanlig grå boks viser navnet på klassen og IDen for bestemt <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.ProxyWebPartManager>kontroll.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.ProxyWebPartManager>

trans-unit.source: You can change the rendering of a custom <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.ProxyWebPartManager> control by overriding the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.WebParts.ProxyWebPartManagerDesigner.GetDesignTimeHtml%2A> method in the same manner as with any standard <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ControlDesigner>.
trans-unit.target: Du kan endre gjengivelse av en egendefinert <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.ProxyWebPartManager>kontrollere ved å overstyre <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.WebParts.ProxyWebPartManagerDesigner.GetDesignTimeHtml%2A>metoden på samme måte som med alle standard <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ControlDesigner>.</xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ControlDesigner> </xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.WebParts.ProxyWebPartManagerDesigner.GetDesignTimeHtml%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.ProxyWebPartManager>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.WebParts.ProxyWebPartManagerDesigner.UsePreviewControl%2A> property is overridden to always return `true`.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.WebParts.ProxyWebPartManagerDesigner.UsePreviewControl%2A>egenskapen overstyres for å returnere alltid `true`.</xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.WebParts.ProxyWebPartManagerDesigner.UsePreviewControl%2A>

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.WebParts.ProxyWebPartManagerDesigner"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: Initialiserer en ny forekomst av den <xref href="System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.WebParts.ProxyWebPartManagerDesigner"> </xref> klasse.

trans-unit.source: Gets an empty string (""), which indicates that the visual design environment should revert to default control rendering.
trans-unit.target: Henter en tom streng (""), noe som angir at utformingsmiljøet i visual må gå tilbake til standard gjengivelse av diagramkontroll.

trans-unit.source: Binds the designer to the associated <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.ProxyWebPartManager"></xref> control.
trans-unit.target: Binding designer til det tilknyttede <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.ProxyWebPartManager"> </xref> kontrollen.

trans-unit.source: The <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.ProxyWebPartManager"></xref> control associated with the designer.
Gets a value indicating whether the designer should use a temporary copy rather than the actual control associated with the designer to generate the design-time markup.
trans-unit.target: Henter en verdi som angir om designer må bruke en midlertidig kopi i stedet for den faktiske kontrollen som er forbundet med designer til å generere utformingen markup.
